W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_004_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_004_DETAIL.text: The cat seems to be unable to climb down from the tree.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_009_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_009_DETAIL.text: A cat is lounging in front of a cozy-looking building.

W01_LTXT_AMYA_HOUSEOFIZUMI_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_LTXT_AMYA_HOUSEOFIZUMI_000_DETAIL.text: Yumeha Izumi's home. Your beloved familiar LoLo waits for you here while you're off at school.

W01_WRLD_AMYA_INITIAL_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_WRLD_AMYA_INITIAL_000_DETAIL.text: You have come to Miyako City for your Witchterms, the passing of which will make you a full-fledged witch.

W01_SCAN_AMYA_INITIAL_WAVE_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_SCAN_AMYA_INITIAL_WAVE_000_DETAIL.text: Someone claiming to be Macha, goddess of sorcery, has given you a magic unlike that which you're familiar with from Pulchra.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_FIRSTCAT_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_FIRSTCAT_000_DETAIL.text: A green line stretches before you. Could it lead you to your magic?

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_001_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_001_DETAIL.text: A cat awaits you on the grounds of a nearby apartment.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_002_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_002_DETAIL.text: A cat awaits in the garden of your home.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_003_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_003_DETAIL.text: A content cat is being petted by the employee of a store near Rakunan Station.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_KUGUTU_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_KUGUTU_000_DETAIL.text: Ren and Kentaro are gossiping about something or other.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_FLOG_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_FLOG_000_DETAIL.text: Ren's got something he wants to tell you.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_FLOG_010_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_FLOG_010_DETAIL.text: The gigantic frog can be found in this pond.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GHOSTSWING_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GHOSTSWING_000_DETAIL.text: Ren and Kentaro are standing near a deserted park.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_RAKUGAKU_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_RAKUGAKU_000_DETAIL.text: The green line leads to Rakugaku Academy. Is it all right to go inside?

W01_EVAR_AMYA_BIRD_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_BIRD_000_DETAIL.text: It's lunch time. What's Kotoha up to?

W01_EVAR_AMYA_HITOKIRI_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_HITOKIRI_000_DETAIL.text: The green line leads to a cat near Miyako Imperial University.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_HITOKIRI_010_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_HITOKIRI_010_DETAIL.text: The cat has absconded toward the cave.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_HITOKIRI_020_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_HITOKIRI_020_DETAIL.text: The cat has absconded toward the cave.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_HITOKIRI_030_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_HITOKIRI_030_DETAIL.text: The sarubobo you found may have something to do with Lifetaker. Head toward the abandoned village.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_HAY_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_HAY_000_DETAIL.text: The classroom is abuzz with information on the latest pollen alert.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_HAY_010_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_HAY_010_DETAIL.text: The source of the pollen seems to be the trees in northeastern part of Miyako City.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_AKANE_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_AKANE_000_DETAIL.text: Yumeha's friends are all done with the music festival. Talk to your teacher before leaving the theater.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_MOVINGTREE_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_MOVINGTREE_000_DETAIL.text: A university student is loitering near Miyako Imperial University.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_MOVINGTREE_010_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_MOVINGTREE_010_DETAIL.text: The green line leads you to the tree Asahi was talking about.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_MYSTERY_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_MYSTERY_000_DETAIL.text: Ren approaches you as you are leaving school.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_MYSTERY_010_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_MYSTERY_010_DETAIL.text: Ren's weird pet is in the river. What's that about?

W01_EVAR_AMYA_KOMAINU_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_KOMAINU_000_DETAIL.text: Something is up in the park. What could be going on?

W01_EVAR_AMYA_MIRROR_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_MIRROR_000_DETAIL.text: You've made plans to meet up with Haruna and Yuzuki at Sequoia Mall, but Yuzuki is running late.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_MIRROR_010_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_MIRROR_010_DETAIL.text: Try to fix the mirror once more.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_005_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_005_DETAIL.text: A cat is sitting next to a worker at the Rakuhoku Station kiosk.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_006_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_006_DETAIL.text: A cat is lazing about in the front lawn of a nearby home.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_007_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_007_DETAIL.text: A cat is sitting on the edge of the road.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_008_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_008_DETAIL.text: A cat is pretending to be a mascot for the nearby store.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_OUTSIDECAT_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_OUTSIDECAT_000_DETAIL.text: The green line leads you to a holy edifice. Is the cat inside?

W01_EVAR_AMYA_RETURN_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_RETURN_000_DETAIL.text: You've gotten mana from another world and have come back to Miyako City.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_010_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_010_DETAIL.text: A cat is staring at the tracks. One wonders if it likes trains.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_011_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_011_DETAIL.text: A cat is napping in a lantern near Rakusuiro Tower. How did it manage that?

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_012_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_012_DETAIL.text: A cat is sitting near a motorcycle. The heat from the engine must be keeping it warm.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_013_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_013_DETAIL.text: A cat is resting in the shade of a tree.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_014_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_014_DETAIL.text: A cat is staring at a nearby building.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_OUTSIDECAT_010_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_OUTSIDECAT_010_DETAIL.text: Yet another line leading to the shrine has appeared.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_015_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_015_DETAIL.text: A cat is playing with a station attendant at Rakuto Station.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_016_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_016_DETAIL.text: A cat is staring at the surface of the water. Did it spy a tasty fish?

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_017_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_017_DETAIL.text: A cat is stumbling about near the trees on hotel grounds. Is it all right?

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_018_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_018_DETAIL.text: A cat is lounging on top of the parapet of the nearby bridge. You can't help but envy its sense of balance.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_019_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_019_DETAIL.text: A cat is having a standoff with a canine competitor on the grounds of a mansion.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_020_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_020_DETAIL.text: A cat in the northeastern outskirts appears to have sensed something.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_021_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_021_DETAIL.text: A cat is loitering about Sequoia Mall.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_OUTSIDECAT_020_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_OUTSIDECAT_020_DETAIL.text: A green line leads to the shrine. What's going on there this time?

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_022_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_022_DETAIL.text: A small cat is hidden betwixt several cramped apartment buildings.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_023_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_023_DETAIL.text: There's a cat perched before the falls at Sangen-in Temple. Said falls, incidentally, are said to bring good luck.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_OUTSIDECAT_030_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_OUTSIDECAT_030_DETAIL.text: Another cat has escaped to a different world...potentially.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_024_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_024_DETAIL.text: Perhaps the cat was tempted by the sound of water in the cave.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_025_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_025_DETAIL.text: A cat is content lounging about Miyako Theater.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_026_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_026_DETAIL.text: A cat is traipsing about the side of a large thoroughfare.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_027_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_GETCAT_027_DETAIL.text: A cat is guarding the path that students traverse each day on their way to school.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_ENDING_60PT_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_ENDING_60PT_000_DETAIL.text: The time has come to pass through the Ama-no-Iwato and return to Pulchra.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_ENDING_80PT_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_ENDING_80PT_000_DETAIL.text: The time has come to pass through the Ama-no-Iwato and return to Pulchra.

W01_EVAR_AMYA_ENDING_100PT_000_DETAIL.speaker: UI
W01_EVAR_AMYA_ENDING_100PT_000_DETAIL.text: The time has come to pass through the Ama-no-Iwato and return to Pulchra.
